, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-14-下午 9.13.01-1748x2048.jpg 1748w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-14-下午 9.13.01.jpg 1366w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 495px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/airpods-pro-service-program-sound-issues">Apple</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
